author: The Current
description:
Jeff Tweedy explains what "Twilight Override" album name means to him
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

During an interview with Jessica Paxton in The Current studio, Jeff Tweedy shares thoughts on the joys and challenges of simply living life.

Jeff Tweedy’s 2025 album, "Twilight Override," is available on dBpm Records.
